card.text:
Whenever this equipment enters, create a 1/1 colorless Spirit creature token, then attach this equipment to that token.
Equipped creature gets +2/+1.
Equip {1}{W}

Whenever this artifact or equipped creature attacks, discard a card then draw a card.
Equipped creature has +2/+1.
Equip {2}

Equipped creature gets +2/+1, has trample, and is an Artificer in addition to its other types.
Whenever this artifact or equipped creature deals combat damage to a player, engineer 2. (Put two +1/+1 counters on an artifact you control. You may have it become a 0/0 artifact creature.)
Equip {1}{R}

When this equipment enters, create two colorless 1/1 Spirit creature tokens. Then this equipment deals damage equal to the number of creatures you control to any target. 
Equipped creature gets +3/+2 and has first strike and menace.
Equip {R}{W}

Destroy target creature that isn't transformed. You lose 2 life.
Cycling {1}{G}
When you cycle this card, Incubate Plants 2. (Create an Incubator token with two +1/+1 counters on it and "{2}: Transform this artifact." It transforms into a 0/0 Plant artifact creature.)
